704205f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Park Place
704205f-a.text:
The intersection of Flatbush Ave. and Park Place at Seventh Ave. The
trolley tracks run northward on Fk tbush Ave. At the left is the Durfey
house, on the corner of Seventh Ave. and Park Place; beyond it appear
Nos. 8-12 Seventh Ave. and the west side of Park P1ace.
About 1912.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

704206f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatbush Avenue - Park Place
704206f-a.text:
319-325 Flatbush Ave., north side, at the intersection of Park
Place and Seventh Ave. In the foreground is a car, the Seventh Ave.
Line and in the background the Flatbush Ave. Line.
November, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
